   388→
   389→    >>> _quotient_and_remainder(36, 24, Unit.DAYS, Unit.HOURS, [], "%0.2f")
   390→    (1, 12)
   391→
   392→    """
   393→    if unit == minimum_unit:
   394→        return _rounding_by_fmt(format, value / divisor), 0
